Package seng202.team4.model

Class DatabaseManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team4.model.DatabaseManager
  • public abstract class DatabaseManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Performs basic interaction with the database that bypasses the errors thrown by the database. Creation of database tables, connection and disconnection to the database and the set up of a database directory on the users machine are performed by the DatabaseManager class.
